summary:
Education Professional and Programme Coordinator for Maastricht University, looking to transition into human rights and legal work. With an LLM @ King's College London, an LLB in European Law, and a Master’s in International Relations,  I have specific knowledge of EU and comparative law, and a special interest in Privacy and Data Protection. 

Privacy and Data Protection as assets! Not simply compliance obligations!
